OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FITV News Political Correspondent Harry
OL,7,FHorton looks at the number of MPs
OL,8,Ffacing criticism for staying on as
OL,9,Fcouncillors. Words by Senior Politics
OL,10,FProducer, Maya Bowles
OL,12,FNearly one in ten MPs are also
OL,13,Fcurrently working as local
OL,14,Fcouncillors, with many still getting
OL,15,Fpaid to do so, new ITV News analysis
OL,16,Fhas found.
