OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FOf the 650 MPs in Parliament, 62 have
OL,7,Fstayed on in their councillor jobs
OL,8,Fsince the general election last year,
OL,9,Fprompting questions whether it's
OL,10,Fpossible to do both jobs
OL,11,Fsimultaneously to a good standard.
OL,13,FITV News analysis shows that of the
OL,14,FMPs whose councillor attendance record
OL,15,Fis public, over half have 50% or less
OL,16,Fattendance at council meetings since
OL,17,F4th July. On top of that, 20% have
OL,18,Fmore than one council role.
