OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FMany of those MPs with council
OL,7,Fpositions have said they plan to give
OL,8,Fup their council role at the next
OL,9,Flocal elections and warn any early
OL,10,Felections triggered by them standing
OL,11,Fdown are costly for the taxpayer.
OL,13,FDespite previously promising to ban
OL,14,Fall second jobs, the Labour government
OL,15,Fhas rowed back on that pledge -
OL,16,Finstead focusing on closing loopholes
OL,17,Fthat allowed politicians to do paid
OL,18,Fadvisory work or consultancy.
