OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FIn the years leading up to the
OL,7,Felection, Labour made their pledge to
OL,8,Fban second jobs for MPs a core part of
OL,9,Ftheir offering to the public -
OL,10,Fpromising change from what they called
OL,11,F"Tory sleaze". In 2021, Starmer
OL,12,Fpledged in a speech to "ban all second
OL,13,Fjobs for MPs, with very limited
OL,14,Fexceptions".
OL,16,FThere is currently a committee looking
OL,17,Finto whether the ban on some second
OL,18,Fjobs should be extended, but ITV News
OL,19,Funderstands councillor jobs aren't
OL,20,Fspecifically being looked at.
