OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FA number of councillors even have more
OL,7,Fthan one council role -
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Labour MPs Michael
OL,9,FPayne and Michelle Welsh both sit
OL,10,Facross two councils, while Labour
OL,11,FForest of Dean MP Matt Bishop also has
OL,12,Ftwo council jobs, South West Norfolk's
OL,13,FLabour MP Terry Jermy has three.
OL,15,FAmong the Lib Dems with more than one
OL,16,Fcouncil job are Freddie Van Mierlo,
OL,17,FLee Dillon and Sarah Gibson.
