OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FWhile others have a council seat in a
OL,7,Ftotally different area to the one they
OL,8,Frepresent as an MP - Labour's Jim
OL,9,FDickson is the MP for Dartford but
OL,10,Fsits on Lambeth Council.
OL,12,FThe Labour rulebook states that when
OL,13,FLabour MPs are elected to parliament
OL,14,Fthey have to give their local council
OL,15,Fseats "on a date agreed with the
OL,16,FCommons Chief Whip and General
OL,17,FSecretary."
