OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FCouncillors are paid around #12,000 a
OL,7,Fyear in what's called an "allowance" -
OL,8,Fit's meant to help cover the cost of
OL,9,Ftime spent on councillor work, rather
OL,10,Fthan acting as a salary. Most
OL,11,Fcouncillors do their local council
OL,12,Fwork alongside another job.
