OL,6,FIf councillors sit on committees, in
OL,7,Fthe council's cabinet, or act as the
OL,8,Fleader of the council - they get extra
OL,9,Fmoney, known as a special
OL,10,Fresponsibility allowance. While most
OL,11,Fof the MPs who did have extra
OL,12,Fresponsibilities have given them up,
OL,13,Fthere are some who are still paid for
OL,14,Fadditional roles.
OL,16,FSome of the highest paid MP
OL,17,Fcouncillors get over #20,000 for their
OL,18,Fcouncil work - taking into account
OL,19,Fadditional roles and positions across
OL,20,Fmultiple councils.
