OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FOf the 62 MPs who are councillors, 30
OL,7,Fare still receiving some kind of
OL,8,Fpayment, on top of the #91,000 a year
OL,9,Fsalary as an MP.
OL,11,FAngela Rayner: 'They will have to
OL,12,Fjustify their ability to do both'
OL,14,FThe majority have given up their
OL,15,Fallowance, either rejecting it
OL,16,Fentirely, donating it to charity, or
OL,17,Fgiving a portion to the local party.
OL,19,FSince the general election on July
OL,20,F4th, many councillors who were elected
OL,21,Fas MPs have stood down..
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
