OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FBut those who haven't say it's because
OL,7,Fif they stepped down it would trigger
OL,8,Fa by-election in their council seat,
OL,9,Fwhich costs extra money for already
OL,10,Fcash-strapped councils, and also means
OL,11,Fvoter turnout is likely to be a lot
OL,12,Flower.
OL,14,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,15,Fsaid staying on as a councillor after
OL,16,Fthe election was "a decision for
OL,17,Findividual MPs", and "they will have
OL,18,Fto justify their ability to do both
OL,19,Fthose jobs".
