OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat Leader Ed Davey said
OL,7,Fhe won't be asking his MPs to stand
OL,8,Fdown, and doing both jobs can actually
OL,9,Fbe positive for democracy: "I think
OL,10,Fpeople who are trying to suggest this
OL,11,Fis a bad thing don't really understand
OL,12,Fhow important it is to be there with
OL,13,Fthe people who elect you and to help
OL,14,Fthem in every way you can."
OL,16,FDavey said it's up to individual MPs
OL,17,Fon what they do, "some will find that
OL,18,Fit's better for them to just focus on
OL,19,Fone issue, others will find that the
OL,20,Ftwo complement each other."
