OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FOxfordshire Council has two Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat MPs who sit on the council -
OL,8,FCalum Miller and Freddie Van Mierlo.
OL,9,FWhile Miller's attendance at meetings
OL,10,Fis 57%, Van Mierlo's is far lower at
OL,11,F25%.
OL,13,FConservative Councillor at Oxfordshire
OL,14,FCouncil Liam Walker called for them to
OL,15,Fstand down, "they've been elected to
OL,16,Fdo a job, by their constituents... If
OL,17,Fyou're not doing that then you're not
OL,18,Fdoing your job as a local councillor,
OL,19,Fso my view is they need to step aside
OL,20,Fand let someone else do it."
