OL,3,COne in ten MPs also sits on a local
OL,4,Ccouncil, ITV News can reveal
OL,6,FITV News spoke to Calum Miller after
OL,7,Fone of the council meetings, which he
OL,8,Fhad attended. He told us "it is
OL,9,Fpossible to combine the roles, it
OL,10,Ftakes a bit of hard work, a bit of
OL,11,Fjetting around and rushing about.
OL,13,F"The critical thing is I think you can
OL,14,Fdo it in a way that really represents
OL,15,Fconstituents well", he said.
OL,17,FWhile Labour and the Lib Dems dominate
OL,18,Fthe list of MPs who are also
OL,19,Fcouncillors, the Conservatives also
OL,20,Fhave six MPs who serve on local
OL,21,Fcouncils.
